title: Port Phillip

Port Phillip was
discovered in 1802 by
John murray. the
indigineous
australians were here
for 40,000 years ago.

it was officially
settled on October
10th 1803. the first
white child was born
on november 25th
1803
the climate is on
average in summer
25 °C {77°F}
occasionally reaching
tempretures of
around and above
40°C {104°F}






it has shallow waters
averaging about 8m. it
is a very popular
thing to visit the
beach because the
tempretures
occasionally get hot
